9  Jopuonjre Yesu nopenje mondo onyisgi tiend ngerono, 
10  

mi nodwokogi niya, “Un osemiu ng’eyo weche mopondo mag Loch Nyasaye. Ji mamoko to ipuonjo mana e yor ngeche, kaka muma wacho ni,

‘Kata da ging’ichi manadi,

to ok ginyal ng’eyo,

bende kata da giwinji,

to wach ok nyal donjonigi.’ ”

